      %h3 Coronavirus Aid, Relief, and Economy Security Act (CARES Act)
      %p
        The CARES Act was signed into law to provide financial “emergency relief” to individuals and businesses caused by the Coronavirus pandemic.  This Act provides relief to:

        %ul
          %li Individuals
          %li Businesses
          %li State and local governments
          %li The health care system

        Below are some of the major provisions in the law for businesses, individuals, stimulus checks, loans, grants and more.
      %br

