      %h3 Families First Coronavirus Response Act (FFCRA)

      %p
        The FFCRA requires certain employers to provide their employees with paid sick leave or expanded family and medical leave for specified reasons related to COVID-19. The Department of Labor’s (Department) Wage and Hour Division (WHD) administers and enforces the new law’s paid leave requirements. These provisions will apply from the effective date through December 31, 2020.
      %p
        Please read
        = link_to "the latest information from the Department of Labor", "https://www.dol.gov/agencies/whd/pandemic/ffcra-employee-paid-leave", target: "_blank"
        as well as our
